Description:
You reach the inner sanctum of the obelisk, but it is too late. Any ritual that has been performed here is already over.

After a quick glance around the room, you can see the body of the princess behind the altar. It seems she is still alive...

Then your eyes focus on the shadowy figure in front of the altar, it is Lord Hanshek, the brooch on his neck glows brightly and a dark energy emanates from it. He looks at you and gives you a sinister smile.
DescriptionAction: The moment of truth has come.
